data.description: One story home with great curb appeal on a quiet street with oversized primary bedroom suite and private backyard; open plan layout, 3 bedrooms all are good sized; roof replaced 5 years ago and has transferable warranty; water heater replaced approx 4 years ago; priced to reflect updates needed. Not in flood zone and no prior flooding, per seller; primary bedroom has bonus space which could be used as home office or converted back to a fourth bedroom; utility room in the house. Real estate is all about location - and this home is great value for a Bear Creek location, Cy Fair ISD, quiet street and easy access to Hwy6/I 10/Hwy 290/Beltway8
